            <text>Velocity of sound in atmosphere v = sqrt( γRT / M ). Oscillations are ____.</text>
            <option id="A">Adiabatic compression-rarefaction</option><option id="B">Isothermal</option>
            <answer>A</answer><explanation>Waves context.</explanation></question>
